Package: rhbsirdata
Title: Tools for Loading and Analyzing Household Budget Survey Iran (HBSIR) Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sana", "Hosseini", 
           email = "hosseinii.sanaa@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-IF-ANY"))
Description: A data package providing convenient functions to load, clean,
    and analyze raw Household Budget Survey (HBS) data from Iran (Statistical Centre of Iran). Includes utilities for 
    expenditures, incomes, sampling weights, household attributes, 
    commodity classifications, and calculation of percentiles, deciles, 
    and quantiles.
